<section class="bg-gray-50 pt-32 pb-24 border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] mb-4">Insurance Coverage</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-500">Stay protected on the road with our comprehensive insurance.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-ink mb-8">Comprehensive Protection Included</h2>
            <p>At Pattaya Rent A Car, safety is our priority. Every vehicle in our fleet is covered by first-class commercial insurance for rental vehicles.</p>
            
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mt-12 mb-6">What is covered?</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-4">
                <li>**Third Party Liability:** Coverage for damage to other vehicles or property.</li>
                <li>**Medical Expense:** Coverage for the driver and passengers in the event of an accident.</li>
                <li>**Collision Damage Waiver (CDW):** Reduces your financial responsibility in case of accidental damage to the rental car.</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="mt-12 p-8 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 rounded-3xl">
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">Excess Levels</h4>
                <p class="text-blue-800 text-sm">Most vehicles have an insurance excess (deductible) of ฿5,000 to ฿10,000. This is the maximum you would pay for damage if you are at fault. Optional "Full Protection" to reduce excess to zero is available at checkout.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Pre-drive checklist callout -->
<section class="py-12 bg-paper border-t border-ink/10">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
    <div class="bg-white border border-ink/10 rounded-2xl px-7 py-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-5">
      <div>
        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary block mb-1">Protect your deposit</span>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-ink tracking-tight m-0">Run the pre-drive checklist first</h2>
        <p class="text-ink/60 text-sm mt-1 mb-0">Before you drive away, take 90 seconds to photograph any existing damage. Our animated guide walks you through all 10 checks — tyres, glass, lights, fuel and more.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="<%= langPrefix %>/pre-drive-checklist/" class="font-mono font-bold text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.1em] bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full whitespace-nowrap transition-colors inline-block">
        View Checklist
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
